      <originalsloc id="aspace_775a12ed0714916e6c2c6729c6cb8985">
         <head>Existence and Location of Originals</head>
         <p>The entire collection can be located in the Harvey Williams Cushing Papers in the Yale University Library (MS 160). The papers are composed of correspondence, subject files, writings, family papers, artifacts, and writings about Harvey Cushing. The papers document the personal life and professional career of a medical giant and pioneer neurosurgeon.</p>
         <p>HM 225: consists of the entire collection with the exception of boxes 71, 74-78, 89-107, 113-119, and 201-205, and the folio.</p>
         <p>HM 241: consists of boxes 89-107, The Brain Tumor Registry</p>  
